# Deploying the Nedia Web Application

This document outlines the plan to deploy the `nedai-web` application (Vite + React) so it is publicly accessible on the internet.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Please review and choose a deployment platform:**
> 
> **Option 1: Vercel (Recommended)**
> Vercel is highly optimized for Vite and React applications. It provides excellent performance, automatic CI/CD from GitHub, and a very generous free tier.
> 
> **Option 2: Render**
> Since your backend (`nedai-server-yrta.onrender.com`) is already hosted on Render, you could host the frontend there as a "Static Site" to keep all your infrastructure in one place.
> 
> **Option 3: Netlify / Cloudflare Pages**
> Similar to Vercel, these are great for static sites.
> 
> *Which platform do you prefer to use?*

## Open Questions

